 statements. He also expressed that he found it &ldquo;out of place&rdquo; that he was being put in the &ldquo;currently very popular racism club&rdquo; for his statements. In contrast with his unapologetic response to Buzzfeed, BAYERN3 and Matthias released an official apology statement that was considerably more contrite just a few hours later.<br />\n<br />\n出完第一個statement死撐<br />\n之後轉頭出多兩個statement死兜道歉"},{"pid":"6cc0b75089dd2604c16e9e0b51b9ad28cebb3efb","tid":2425368,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"好波！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60267f557536dff556faa3ed4714aeae9f653ed3","tid":2425368,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:27:41.000Z","msg":"講下笑都俾人屈種族歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13640d560636a7e990a24c3f7669dc52e8da0a9","tid":2425368,"uid":377697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"港豬: 外國人只會歧視支那人, 對其他亞洲人好好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}